{"id": 756, "genre": 1001, "title": "一句话说明你是颜控？", "description": "是的，我就是玩游戏也一定要玩截个图就能当壁纸那种，的人。（题图来自：HELENA PEREZ GARCIA）", "record_count": 7408, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183548l3GaoN79vuPjqRsi.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-01-30T01:05:27Z", "options": [{"id": 45056, "content": "美貌即美德?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 438353}, {"id": 45824, "content": "看一眼后，什么都可以不用再说，或者有太多话说……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 451874}, {"id": 45058, "content": "曾经怀疑过自己的性取向", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428045}, {"id": 45826, "content": "外貌和身材决定了我要不要去探究她的智慧与内涵，而智慧与内涵决定了我是不是要否决她的外貌和身材", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 389563}, {"id": 53250, "content": "App图标要好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 217883}, {"id": 45059, "content": "噢（有根头发翘出来了）“请问卫生间在哪里”", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 344979}, {"id": 45060, "content": "照镜子会心塞", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447158}, {"id": 45062, "content": "买电子产品时不看性能 看颜", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 412141}, {"id": 45064, "content": "因为王源喜欢上了之前看不上的TFboys", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004756sNDjLTpCVxmRnh8Q.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447162}, {"id": 45321, "content": "从小就没和比自己丑的人交朋友  ！长大后全部断交了 因为小时候美的人长大了基本都丑 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449139}, {"id": 45833, "content": "丑逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422331}, {"id": 45068, "content": "Why so serious", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004804tNLWFZbuTrz5v1Eg.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 337611}, {"id": 45837, "content": "好看的APP封面就算内容辣鸡也舍不得删\n有一次把APP封面小清新还小众的放一个文件夹里各种炫耀各种得意哈?就是颜控", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 451940}, {"id": 46093, "content": "不吃猪肉……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453126}, {"id": 45070, "content": "找对象说 看感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447179}, {"id": 45071, "content": "颜值是必然", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447180}, {"id": 45327, "content": "什么鬼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449282}, {"id": 45073, "content": "只要有能当镜子的地方，我都会情不自禁，然后明白很多道理", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 446763}, {"id": 45329, "content": "长得好看的才给道歉，丑的一概是对方的错。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 443779}, {"id": 45074, "content": "从一堆漫画集挑封面好看的看", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 440398}, {"id": 45075, "content": "我是天秤座", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 440398}, {"id": 45332, "content": "你这么好看，你说什么都对", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112264}, {"id": 49940, "content": "整那么丑出来得瑟啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469401}, {"id": 52500, "content": "長成這個樣子，跟你XXOO還不如去死……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 354380}, {"id": 45077, "content": "郭敬明不矮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447205}, {"id": 45078, "content": "眼里两种人，颜高，颜low", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447195}, {"id": 45080, "content": "先看脸，再走心", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241724}, {"id": 45336, "content": "自己丑可以，别人不能丑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 433400}, {"id": 45337, "content": ".", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449453}, {"id": 45084, "content": "打人不打脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 298073}, {"id": 45343, "content": "kkw", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449539}, {"id": 46880, "content": "我喜欢女友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456691}, {"id": 45090, "content": "因为我是单身狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447425}, {"id": 45350, "content": "不喜欢妹子穿丝袜，原来穿丝袜的妹子这么漂亮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 433391}, {"id": 45352, "content": "再爱也不回头。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449628}, {"id": 45097, "content": "啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447524}, {"id": 45356, "content": "新買的手機一定下載一張自己喜歡的圖片當桌面⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 383972}, {"id": 45101, "content": "外表好其他都无所谓", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447553}, {"id": 45102, "content": "光唱得好不行，还要有黄致列的颜  原来同时颜控声控性格控可以在一个人身上实现 哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 4119}, {"id": 45103, "content": "不好看的直接连话都不想说了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 47770}, {"id": 46898, "content": "只要颜值高，剧情什么的都不重要的啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456710}, {"id": 45619, "content": "这菜长得太丑不想吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 414406}, {"id": 45108, "content": "沒錢可以必須帥", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447606}, {"id": 45364, "content": "不可燃垃圾", "image": "img/option/option/20160606000655jZr5ivnSbV0N2h7R.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449719}, {"id": 45111, "content": "平常都不敢多照镜子…怕被自己美哭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfec